<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#000000"><td><font color="#FFFFFF"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">Oooooh...a MONEY deck!</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">yodamuppet</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Uses the combined strengths (and combos) of the Uruk-hai and Nazgul to kick Frodo&#39;s arse.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">STARTING:<br />
<!--175-->Frodo, Son of Drogo<br />
<!--96-->The One Ring, Isildur&#39;s Bane<br />
<br />
SITES:<br />
[1] <!--205-->The Prancing Pony<br />
